        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Shimeah - Called Shamma (marginal reference), was Jesse's third son.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Subtil - literally, wise. The word is generally used in a good sense, but here, and in Job 5:13, it means crafty. ",
        "children": [
